---
import Main from "@/layouts/Main.astro";
---

<Main title="About | Bible Games">
  <section class="panel">
    <h1 class="title">About Bible Games</h1>

    <p>
      Bible Games helps kids and families turn scripture chapters into printable activities that are simple to use at
      home, church, and school.
    </p>

    <p>
      Current games include chapter-based word searches and verse cryptograms. We plan to keep adding more printable
      game types over time.
    </p>

    <p>
      Bible text displayed on this site comes from a local copy of the Berean Standard Bible (BSB).
    </p>
  </section>
</Main>
